{"tid":334372,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】開埋今晚去旅行 Day75 24/7","createTime":"2017-07-24T15:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T18:40:01.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fa3c7f9c945dd91e2f47a66d2952e3c9b027168","tid":334372,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:28:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=axfG9w7FiuduG36e9geNTk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=6e69bf75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=axfG9w7FiuduG36e9geNTk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d5f2d582\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=axfG9w7FiuduG36e9geNTk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=687570ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"5177a4c6d2c2fab2c2320b6e4a2cabc7cab91bb7","tid":334372,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823e75056cddd3783d3a3fce6ab48a3aa2a94099","tid":334372,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173c90cf1d413cca7e909a09b609a466b2668bbf","tid":334372,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8073aa9151c7cca2ff3d603f60de6165e10472b","tid":334372,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a444a2cc53894982a5399b39564c1d8e9c085bc4","tid":334372,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0037ca72fe0a9f4165a82509402df5ff0c3649c","tid":334372,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546d01b35528d877d00b10f676491a2544c9afb1","tid":334372,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d22f05910cda15399bc30ee558786d85f10843","tid":334372,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmo